videos.description: Ryan Mutombo tries to dunk it home, but Adama Sanogo swats it away for UConn.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (No, no, no! Sanogo stuffs Mutombo at the rim) 2022/01/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: No, no, no! Sanogo stuffs Mutombo at the rim

videos.description: Georgetown brings the pressure against UConn, but the Huskies advance the ball to Isaiah Whaley for a two-handed jam.

videos.headline: Whaley dunks it home as UConn breaks the press with ease

videos.description: Andre Jackson tees up Adama Sanogo for an alley-oop to give UConn a 24-point lead over Georgetown.
